01:16.554 --> 01:17.990
White Diamond: Once upon a time,

01:17.990 --> 01:21.603
the Gem Homeworld
was ruled by Diamonds --

01:21.603 --> 01:24.171
White, Yellow, Blue,

01:24.171 --> 01:27.652
and the littlest Diamond, Pink.

01:27.652 --> 01:29.915
While the other Diamonds
conquered many worlds

01:29.915 --> 01:31.395
across the galaxy,

01:31.395 --> 01:35.747
Pink had only one --
the planet Earth.

01:35.747 --> 01:39.534
One day, Pink fled
the comforts of Homeworld.

01:39.534 --> 01:43.407
On Earth, she made a new home,
new friends,

01:43.407 --> 01:45.757
and finally, new life,

01:45.757 --> 01:47.411
