put me on a throne.

02:29.236 --> 02:31.934
I already have a rightful place,
and it's on Earth.

02:31.934 --> 02:34.806
Huh?What?

02:34.806 --> 02:36.982
It's a beach house,
where I live with my friends,

02:36.982 --> 02:38.941
Garnet, Amethyst, and Pearl.

02:38.941 --> 02:41.248
As much as I've loved
dismantling the Empire

02:41.248 --> 02:44.076
and saving all your planets,
I can't wait to get home

02:44.076 --> 02:48.255
and spend some quality time
with my friends.

02:48.255 --> 02:49.604
