Steven!
I came as fast as I could!

16:21.415 --> 16:22.938
Are you okay?

16:22.938 --> 16:25.941
Holy s-s-she really
got everybody!

16:25.941 --> 16:28.074
Is that her?
Yeah.

16:28.074 --> 16:29.727
Who --
No idea.

16:29.727 --> 16:31.599
Why?
No idea.

16:31.599 --> 16:32.817
How?

16:32.817 --> 16:35.385
She hit all of us
with this.

16:35.385 --> 16:37.779
Waah!

16:37.779 --> 16:40.260
Phew.It did something
extra weird to me,

16:40.260 --> 16:42.131
and now my powers
aren't working right.

16:42.131 --> 16:43.263
Look.

16:45.352 --> 16:47.136
There's something wrong
with me, Dad.

16:49.747 --> 16:52.141
I just have no idea
what's going on.

16:52.141 --> 16:55.710
Well, son, now you know
how I feel almost all the time.

16:55.710 --> 16:57.146
But you know what else?

16:57.146 --> 16:59.583
Any moment now, the Gems
are gonna do that thing

16:59.583 --> 17:01.498
where they glow
and float in the air

17:01.498 --> 17:03.283
and reappear
better than ever.

17:03.283 --> 17:04.327
Huh?

17:04.327 --> 17:05.807
See? Here she comes.

17:05.807 --> 17:08.940
Good old Pearl.

17:08.940 --> 17:10.986
Huh.
Well, that's new.

17:10.986 --> 17:13.380
Pearl:
Please identify yourself.

17:13.380 --> 17:16.078
Um, Greg Universe?

17:16.078 --> 17:18.428
Greetings, Um Greg Universe.

17:18.428 --> 17:21.648
Please state preferred
customization options.

17:21.648 --> 17:24.260
Uh...
What am I supposed to say here?

17:24.260 --> 17:25.827
I-I don't know.

17:25.827 --> 17:27.481
Default setting selected.

17:27.481 --> 17:29.135
Please stand by.

17:29.135 --> 17:36.185
♪♪

17:36.185 --> 17:43.236
♪♪

17:43.236 --> 17:44.498
Pearl!

17:44.498 --> 17:46.108
Pearl, thank goodness
you're back!

17:46.108 --> 17:47.457
Huh?

17:47.457 --> 17:50.373
Pearl?

17:50.373 --> 17:52.810
♪ How do you do? ♪

17:52.810 --> 17:55.204
♪ My "Um Greg Universe" ♪

17:55.204 --> 18:00.035
♪ Thank you for bringing me
into the world ♪

18:00.035 --> 18:04.344
♪ I am at your eternal service ♪

18:04.344 --> 18:07.825
♪ Welcome to your new Pearl ♪

18:07.825 --> 18:09.914
♪♪

18:09.914 --> 18:12.482
Wha-a-at's going on?!Wha-a-at's going on?!

18:12.482 --> 18:15.703
Could her gem
be cracked?

18:15.703 --> 18:17.357
It looks fine to me.

18:17.357 --> 18:22.492
♪♪

18:22.492 --> 18:25.060
Ruby!
Are -- Are you okay?

18:25.060 --> 18:26.757
Aah!
Who are you?

18:26.757 --> 18:28.324
You're not my assignment.

18:28.324 --> 18:30.544
I could really use
an explanation here.

18:30.544 --> 18:33.373
Allow me to illuminate.

18:33.373 --> 18:35.679
♪ A Ruby guard ♪

18:35.679 --> 18:38.204
♪ But just a single one ♪

18:38.204 --> 18:42.033
♪ They tend to come in teams
of three or more ♪

18:42.033 --> 18:43.078
[ Gasps ]

18:43.078 --> 18:45.254
♪ A precious Sapphire ♪

18:45.254 --> 18:47.387
♪ She sees the future ♪

18:47.387 --> 18:50.781
♪ That's who
the Ruby's for ♪

18:50.781 --> 18:52.131
My Sapphire.

18:52.131 --> 18:54.437
As my sworn duty
and sole purpose,

18:54.437 --> 18:56.874
I will protect you
with my life.

18:56.874 --> 18:58.963
I know you will.
That's why I predict

18:58.963 --> 19:00.922
you won't last
more than a day.

19:00.922 --> 19:02.967
Huh?
Come, now.

19:02.967 --> 19:07.929
♪♪

19:07.929 --> 19:10.714
Amethyst! Hey --
Amethyst?

19:10.714 --> 19:12.151
Hey -- Amethyst?

19:12.151 --> 19:14.153
What? No.
You're Amethyst.

19:14.153 --> 19:16.590
What? No.
You're Amethyst.

19:16.590 --> 19:18.896
♪ You must be right ♪

19:18.896 --> 19:21.421
♪ This is an Amethyst ♪

19:21.421 --> 19:26.121
♪ Except an Amethyst
is big and strong ♪

19:26.121 --> 19:30.560
♪ This one is not
the best example ♪

19:30.560 --> 19:35.739
♪ Something is
clearly wrong ♪

19:35.739 --> 19:39.482
I do say,
something isclearly wrong.

19:39.482 --> 19:41.484
What are all these
different Gems doing here

19:41.484 --> 19:43.269
in this strange place?

19:43.269 --> 19:45.271
Pearl, don't you
recognize them?

19:45.271 --> 19:46.794
Don't you recognize me?

19:46.794 --> 19:49.144
Hmm.

19:49.144 --> 19:52.626
Well, I certainly recognize
my Um Greg Universe.

19:52.626 --> 19:54.193
Oh, boy.

19:54.193 --> 19:57.108
As for you...hmm.

19:57.108 --> 19:58.675
Huh?

19:58.675 --> 20:01.156
♪♪

20:01.156 --> 20:02.201
Get back!

20:02.201 --> 20:05.247
Huh?

20:05.247 --> 20:06.814
[ Giggling ]

20:06.814 --> 20:09.773
Yippee!

20:09.773 --> 20:12.298
I'm so excited to meet you!

20:12.298 --> 20:14.430
Y-You're not mad?

20:14.430 --> 20:16.693
Mad? Why would I be mad

20:16.693 --> 20:19.522
at my best friend!

20:19.522 --> 20:21.655
[ Giggling ]

20:21.655 --> 20:24.005
♪ This will be fun ♪

20:24.005 --> 20:26.399
♪ Aren't you the lucky one? ♪

20:26.399 --> 20:31.055
[ Squeaking ]♪ Her cut is perfect,
and she's pink, as well ♪

20:31.055 --> 20:35.582
♪ She'll bring you
endless entertainment ♪

20:35.582 --> 20:39.150
♪ Your new best friend, Spinel ♪

20:39.150 --> 20:42.850
♪♪

20:42.850 --> 20:44.808
You!!

20:44.808 --> 20:46.897
What have you done to us?[ Squeak! Squeak! Squeak! ]

20:46.897 --> 20:48.159
[ Giggles ]

20:48.159 --> 20:52.033
Boop!
Now it's your turn!

20:52.033 --> 20:53.774
[ Giggling ][ Groaning ]

20:53.774 --> 20:57.517
W-W-W-Would you
cut that out?

20:57.517 --> 20:59.432
[ Gasping ]

20:59.432 --> 21:02.652
Please?

21:02.652 --> 21:04.654
Hey, look!

21:04.654 --> 21:07.178
There's more Gems!

21:07.178 --> 21:08.919
Let's ask 'em to play.

21:08.919 --> 21:10.356
W-Wait a minute.

21:10.356 --> 21:11.879
You don't remember?

21:11.879 --> 21:13.359
Remember what?

21:16.579 --> 21:19.060
Wowee!

21:19.060 --> 21:21.410
That thing sure is big!

21:21.410 --> 21:23.325
[ Squeaking ]You wanna climb it or somethin'?

21:23.325 --> 21:26.285
Wait, wait.
Are you serious right now?

21:26.285 --> 21:27.895
What about
that stuff you said

21:27.895 --> 21:30.811
about how I won't stand a chance
against your injector?

21:30.811 --> 21:32.726
I said what now?

21:32.726 --> 21:36.425
You really
don't remember, huh?

21:36.425 --> 21:37.687
How 'bout you, Lion?

21:37.687 --> 21:39.080
Can you make
any sense of this?

21:39.080 --> 21:40.560
[ Roars ]

21:40.560 --> 21:42.866
Aw, you're no help, either.

21:42.866 --> 21:45.304
At least I can store this thing
in your mane.

21:47.654 --> 21:49.917
I can't store things
in Lion's mane now?

21:49.917 --> 21:52.311
That's like
the easiest thing I do!

21:54.922 --> 21:56.184
What do I do?

21:56.184 --> 21:57.664
I've got no friends to help me,

21:57.664 --> 22:00.362
except...

22:00.362 --> 22:02.451
Bismuth, Lapis, and Peridot.

22:02.451 --> 22:04.932
Come on, guys. Let's go
figure out how to fix this.

22:04.932 --> 22:07.195
[ Laughing ]G-Guys?

22:07.195 --> 22:10.198
My Um Greg, allow me.

22:10.198 --> 22:12.505
[ Groans ]

22:12.505 --> 22:15.377
Hmm.
Mm-hmm. Hmm.

22:15.377 --> 22:17.553
Ruby? Sapphire?

22:17.553 --> 22:19.947
She's not going anywhere
with you.

22:19.947 --> 22:22.732
I do see us following him
to the countryside.

22:22.732 --> 22:24.604
Never mind! We're going.

22:24.604 --> 22:27.955
Wait. Don't leave me alone
with these two!

22:27.955 --> 22:29.130
Just keep an eye
on them for now.

22:29.130 --> 22:30.261
I'll be back.

22:30.261 --> 22:33.308
[ Squeak! Squeak! Squeak! ]

22:33.308 --> 22:35.919
♪♪

22:35.919 --> 22:38.357
She rode in on that?!

22:38.357 --> 22:40.924
Yeah.
She said my human half

22:40.924 --> 22:43.971
wouldn't stand a chance
against her injector.

22:43.971 --> 22:45.625
What does that mean?

22:45.625 --> 22:47.322
Why don't we
just ask her?

22:47.322 --> 22:48.497
[ Ruby growls ]

22:48.497 --> 22:50.325
Well, here's the thing.

22:50.325 --> 22:52.066
Hmm? What?[ Squeak! Squeak! ]

22:52.066 --> 22:53.197
Where'd she -- Aah![ Squeak! ]

22:53.197 --> 22:55.286
Surprise!
[ Laughs ]

22:55.286 --> 22:58.638
Here she is,
my new best friend, Spinel.

22:58.638 --> 23:01.467
A pleasure to meet you all.

23:01.467 --> 23:03.860
I thought you said she was
just trying to kill you.

23:03.860 --> 23:06.254
Wow. Quick turnaround.No kidding.

23:06.254 --> 23:08.691
It took me months to stop
trying to kill Steven.

23:08.691 --> 23:11.172
I say it took me a day,
day and a half?

23:11.172 --> 23:14.001
I'm still on the fence.[ Laughter ]

23:14.001 --> 23:16.351
Alright, let's see this thing
she hit you with.

23:16.351 --> 23:18.745
Uh, right.

23:18.745 --> 23:21.008
Whoa. Was there, like,
a laser or --

23:21.008 --> 23:22.662
Be careful with that.

23:22.662 --> 23:25.926
It's a rejuvenator.

23:25.926 --> 23:27.406
Homeworld used to use
these things

23:27.406 --> 23:29.669
on Gems that started
steppin' out of line.

23:29.669 --> 23:32.236
One hit with this...

23:32.236 --> 23:34.021
you're back
to how they made you.

23:34.021 --> 23:36.284
What are you lookin' at?

23:36.284 --> 23:39.156
Oh, my stars,
I touched it!

23:39.156 --> 23:41.550
I could have lost
all my character development.

23:41.550 --> 23:45.815
Wait, how did yousurvive
being hit by that thing, Steven?

23:45.815 --> 23:48.035
I-I think I didn't.

23:48.035 --> 23:50.385
My human half kept me
from poofing, but --

23:50.385 --> 23:52.648
but my Gem half,
it took the hit.

23:52.648 --> 23:54.911
She sent me back.
It's like I'm a kid again.

23:54.911 --> 23:57.044
I can barely
control my powers.

23:57.044 --> 23:58.698
How do we reverse this?

23:58.698 --> 23:59.873
Oh, no.

23:59.873 --> 24:01.527
Do I need
to get the Diamonds?

24:01.527 --> 24:03.137
You're the one
with healing powers.

24:03.137 --> 24:06.227
If anyone can fix this,
it's you.

24:06.227 --> 24:07.924
I can't believe this.

24:07.924 --> 24:10.840
For the first time in years,
everyone's in danger.

24:10.840 --> 24:14.975
Everybody needs me,
and I'm useless.

24:14.975 --> 24:17.499
Bismuth, what do we do?

24:17.499 --> 24:19.196
I'm sorry, Steven.

24:19.196 --> 24:20.894
I don't know.

24:20.894 --> 24:23.592
♪♪

24:23.592 --> 24:25.638
Steven:
Garnet would know what to do.

24:25.638 --> 24:28.423
Garnet always
knows what to do.

24:28.423 --> 24:30.294
Hey, don't be sad!

24:30.294 --> 24:32.993
♪ Your new best friend,
your new best friend ♪

24:32.993 --> 24:35.212
Your new best friend!
Your new best friend,

24:35.212 --> 24:37.084
Spinel, is here!

24:37.084 --> 24:40.304
[ Laughing rhythmically ]

24:40.304 --> 24:42.176
[ Squeaking ]

24:45.048 --> 24:47.964
♪ Here we are in the future ♪

24:47.964 --> 24:53.535
♪ Here we are in the future,
and it's wrong ♪

24:53.535 --> 24:58.627
♪ Just a second ago,
we were singing this song ♪

24:58.627 --> 25:01.630
♪ And now they're gone ♪

25:01.630 --> 25:05.939
♪ Because of her ♪

25:05.939 --> 25:11.771
♪ Happily ever after,
there we were ♪

25:11.771 --> 25:14.251
♪ When has it ever
been easy? ♪

25:14.251 --> 25:18.125
♪ Hasn't it always been hard
to be us? ♪

25:18.125 --> 25:21.694
♪♪

25:21.694 --> 25:24.435
♪ When you go
against the grain ♪

25:24.435 --> 25:28.309
♪ There's always somebody around
you can't trust ♪

25:28.309 --> 25:31.355
♪♪

25:31.355 --> 25:34.315
♪ That's why we've
got to have each other ♪

25:34.315 --> 25:36.839
♪ Why, we'll figure this out,
we must ♪

25:36.839 --> 25:42.018
♪ Because we
are the Crystal Gems ♪

25:42.018 --> 25:46.849
♪ And we never give up, we never
give up on our friends ♪

25:46.849 --> 25:51.985
♪ As long as one of us is
standing to brandish the star ♪

25:51.985 --> 25:54.553
♪ We'll find a way
to save the day ♪

25:54.553 --> 25:58.339
♪ That's who we are ♪

25:58.339 --> 26:00.950
♪ Here we are in the future ♪

26:00.950 --> 26:06.173
♪ Here we are in the future,
and it's wrong ♪

26:06.173 --> 26:10.090
♪ Look at them, they're not
even singing along ♪

26:10.090 --> 26:15.530
♪ If I coulda just stopped
right there, we'd be ♪

26:15.530 --> 26:20.448
♪ Totally fine,
totally us, totally me ♪

26:20.448 --> 26:23.320
♪ Even if it takes a thousand
years to get them back ♪

26:23.320 --> 26:25.540
♪ We will ♪

26:25.540 --> 26:30.806
♪ They may not know
who they are, but we do ♪

26:30.806 --> 26:33.461
♪ Believe me, Steven,
I've known them longer ♪

26:33.461 --> 26:36.856
♪ I've seen them get through
worse and come back stronger ♪

26:36.856 --> 26:41.208
♪ That's why I believe in them,
and I believe in you ♪

26:41.208 --> 26:46.082
♪ Because we
are the Crystal Gems ♪

26:46.082 --> 26:51.305
♪ And we never give up, no, we
never give up on our friends ♪

26:51.305 --> 26:56.397
♪ As long as one of us is
standing to brandish the star ♪

26:56.397 --> 26:57.703
♪ We'll find a way ♪♪ We'll find a way ♪

26:57.703 --> 26:59.008
♪ To save the day ♪

26:59.008 --> 27:02.055
♪ That's who we are ♪

27:02.055 --> 27:03.578
Right. Okay.

27:03.578 --> 27:05.101
Let's put our heads together.

27:05.101 --> 27:07.234
There's gotta be some way
to make them remember.

27:07.234 --> 27:09.410
What if it's like a puzzle?Huh?

27:09.410 --> 27:11.586
If we give 'em
all the pieces,

27:11.586 --> 27:13.588
eventually,
they'll get the picture.

27:13.588 --> 27:16.330
Spinel, you might
be onto something.

27:16.330 --> 27:19.594
If every experience they lost
is a-a piece of who they are,

27:19.594 --> 27:21.683
we just have to give them back
all the pieces,

27:21.683 --> 27:23.250
one experience at a time.

27:23.250 --> 27:24.381
Are you serious?

27:24.381 --> 27:25.992
That could take forever!

27:25.992 --> 27:28.777
Exactly.
So, let's get started.

27:28.777 --> 27:32.999
♪ We'll find a way to save
the day, that's who we are ♪

27:35.088 --> 27:37.090
♪ Here we are
in the future ♪

27:37.090 --> 27:39.179
Yeah!
♪ Here we are in the future ♪

27:39.179 --> 27:42.182
♪ And it's wrong ♪

27:42.182 --> 27:44.837
Whoa, Spinel, it's okay.
We're done.

27:46.926 --> 27:48.579
Hup, hup, hup, hup.

27:48.579 --> 27:50.407
Mm-hmm.

27:50.407 --> 27:52.366
Hup, hup, hup, hup,
hup, hup, hup, hup.

27:52.366 --> 27:55.761
So, when Ruby and Sapphire
first became Garnet,

27:55.761 --> 27:57.937
Ruby rushed in
to save Sapphire from danger,

27:57.937 --> 27:59.895
and bam -- They fused.

27:59.895 --> 28:01.636
So, maybe we've gotta create

28:01.636 --> 28:03.507
some sort of
dangerous situation.

28:03.507 --> 28:04.813
Well, what do we have

28:04.813 --> 28:06.772
that's deadly
and dangerous laying around?

28:06.772 --> 28:09.252
I think we could
dig something up.

28:09.252 --> 28:10.863
[ Chuckles ]

28:10.863 --> 28:13.039
Danger, danger, danger.

28:13.039 --> 28:14.475
What have we got?

28:14.475 --> 28:16.433
Hmm. No.

28:16.433 --> 28:18.174
[ Gasps ] Aha!

28:18.174 --> 28:19.872
A giant pizza cutter?

28:19.872 --> 28:22.265
That is one of its
functions, yes.

28:22.265 --> 28:24.006
I can't threaten them
with this.

28:24.006 --> 28:26.530
Hmm. Here.

28:26.530 --> 28:28.315
Now it's much
more threatening.

28:28.315 --> 28:29.751
Off you go, now.

28:29.751 --> 28:31.405
Good luck!

28:31.405 --> 28:34.495
Hup, hup, hup, hup,
hup, hup, hup.

28:34.495 --> 28:36.062
Hup, hup, hup, hup.

28:36.062 --> 28:37.628
Hmm? Halt!

28:37.628 --> 28:39.500
I cannot allow you
to approach my Sapphire

28:39.500 --> 28:41.676
with such
a threatening device.

28:41.676 --> 28:45.985
That's too bad,
'cause I'm gonna...get you!

28:45.985 --> 28:48.161
Will this work?[ Giggles ]

28:48.161 --> 28:50.729
Permission to dispatch the
curly-haired one, my Sapphire?

28:50.729 --> 28:54.036
No need. I predict he won't
be able to follow through.

28:54.036 --> 28:55.777
She's right.

28:55.777 --> 28:58.171
Ugh, I can't.

28:58.171 --> 29:00.869
Even if we are
just pretending.

29:00.869 --> 29:03.002
My Sapphire,
you were right!

29:03.002 --> 29:04.960
What do you predict
will happen next?

29:04.960 --> 29:09.399
Well, the Spinel will pick up
that device out of curiosity.

29:09.399 --> 29:10.661
Hmm.

29:10.661 --> 29:12.968
Hijinks will ensue.

29:12.968 --> 29:14.404
Maybe we should try --

29:14.404 --> 29:16.537
Wait, Spinel.
No, no, no, no!

29:16.537 --> 29:19.845
Don't touch that thing!

29:19.845 --> 29:22.195
[ Crash ]Hey, we just built that!

29:22.195 --> 29:23.239
[ Screaming ]

29:23.239 --> 29:24.545
[ Crash ]

29:24.545 --> 29:27.069
[ Continues screaming ]

29:27.069 --> 29:29.724
Whoa, here she comes!

29:29.724 --> 29:31.117
Spinel!

29:31.117 --> 29:37.166
♪♪

29:37.166 --> 29:38.733
My scaffolding.

29:38.733 --> 29:41.605
My precious scaffolding!

29:41.605 --> 29:43.259
Wow!
What happens next?

29:43.259 --> 29:44.739
In just a moment,

29:44.739 --> 29:47.524
the scaffolding will start
falling all around you.

29:47.524 --> 29:49.570
What?

29:49.570 --> 29:51.702
Hup!

29:51.702 --> 29:53.704
Wow.
You're amazing!

29:53.704 --> 29:56.490
Hmph. Next,
the Peridot will hold back

29:56.490 --> 29:57.926
some of the falling debris.

29:57.926 --> 29:59.754
Three large barrels
will fall.

29:59.754 --> 30:01.800
The Bismuth will catch
two of them.

30:01.800 --> 30:03.062
I got this, Biz!

30:03.062 --> 30:06.021
Nice work, Perido--
Oh, shucks!

30:06.021 --> 30:07.806
Ah. Shoot!

30:07.806 --> 30:10.504
Oh, no! The Heaven
and Earth Beetles

30:10.504 --> 30:12.898
are out for their afternoon
constitutional!

30:12.898 --> 30:15.857
Sapphire:
The Lapis will rush in and
save them at the last second.

30:15.857 --> 30:18.686
♪♪

30:18.686 --> 30:20.819
Whew.
You guys okay?

30:25.519 --> 30:28.304
Whoa.
Is it...over?

30:28.304 --> 30:29.523
The saw.

30:29.523 --> 30:32.918
The saw
will continue to cut.

30:32.918 --> 30:34.571
The anvil will fall.

30:34.571 --> 30:37.531
♪♪

30:37.531 --> 30:41.970
And you --
you will be shattered.

30:41.970 --> 30:43.624
Huh? Aah!

30:43.624 --> 30:46.148
♪♪

30:46.148 --> 30:47.323
Huh?

30:47.323 --> 30:48.934
[ Straining ]

30:48.934 --> 30:51.240
The curly-haired one's power
is fading.

30:51.240 --> 30:54.156
♪♪

30:54.156 --> 30:56.376
